# Student Management System (C Language)

## 📖 Description
This is a simple Student Management System built using C programming language. It allows users to add, display, and search student records using a menu-driven program.

## 🚀 Features
- Add Student
- Display Students
- Search Student
- Menu-driven system

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- C Programming
- Structures
- Arrays

## ▶️ How to Run
1. Copy code into any C compiler
2. Compile and run the program
3. Use menu options (Add / Display / Search)

